					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I put Keter because there is a small (but nonzero!) chance of anyone in the world with a car doing this on accident, and that can't be prevented at least until the Foundation finishes up the containment procedures and cars are all eventually incapable of using it.</p> <p>If you can argue for it being Safe or Euclid, I'm all ears.</p> 
				 	]]>
